<div id="text"><div class="LC" id="left">
<p>Home loan financing is a snap when you <a href="../MortgageApplication/LoanAppShort.htm">
apply online</a>, even with bad credit. Have great credit? So much the
better. We will look at your individual situation as a starting
point, not as a way to disqualify you. Our liberal credit guidelines
allow us to offer mortgage loans to those with good or bad credit. Refinancing
your home loan, even with <a href="http://www.lightning-mortgage.com/CreditScores.htm">
bad credit</a>, is easy with Lightning Mortgage. <a
href="http://www.lightning-mortgage.com/MortgageApplication/LoanAppShort.htm">Applying online</a>
for a loan is convenient. Simply answer a few questions about yourself and your property and let us
do the rest.</p>
<p>Look around this site before filling out
the application. Learn about how we work, the information required for
refinancing or purchasing, and about how <a href="http://www.lightning-mortgage.com/CreditScores.htm">credit
scores</a> affect the loans available to you. Get your questions answered
about <a href="http://www.lightning-mortgage.com/Answers/WhatsInvolved.htm">what's
involved</a> with the online loan process, and the various mortgage <a
class="Index" href="http://www.lightning-mortgage.com/LoanTypes.php">loan types</a> available. Use our
mortgage <a href="http://www.lightning-mortgage.com/Administrative/Calculators.htm">calculators</a>
to see how interest rates and loan amounts will change your monthly
payment. You'll find us to be both knowledgeable and helpful. When you're ready to apply, go ahead and
fill out a <a href="http://www.lightning-mortgage.com/MortgageApplication/LoanAppShort.htm">Loan
Application</a>, 24 hours a day, 7 days a week. It is just that simple.</p>
<p>This site is not just a convenient place to make a mortgage finance or refinance request and hope
that you're making the right decision and will obtain the lowest possible
<a href="http://www.lightning-mortgage.com/InterestRates.htm">interest rate</a>.</p>
</div><div class="RC" id="right">
<p>You can be certain that we are experts at determining the lowest cost loan
based upon the information you provide. We'll advise you of your options so that you, once and for
all, can make the best choice. And sometimes we come across a situation
where it doesn't make sense to refinance. If that's the case, we'll tell you.</p>

<blockquote class="PullQuote">
     Have errors on your report? Click to read about <a href="../CreditScores/CorrectingMistakes.htm">how to fix mistakes</a>
     on your credit report.
</blockquote>
<p>Not ready to make that big step of filling out an
<a href="../MortgageApplication/LoanAppShort.htm">application</a>?
A mortgage is the biggest debt most people ever have, so we understand
your need to feel comfortable with making a change. We want your experience with us to be a great one.
Knowing more about mortgage financing will help you make better decisions. Read through our
<a href="http://www.lightning-mortgage.com//Answers.php">answers</a>
to questions we frequently have asked. Our
<a href="http://www.lightning-mortgage.com/Answers/GlossaryAD.htm">Glossary</a>
defines frequently heard mortgage terms.</p>
<p>We also have a free gift where you can learn the secrets for breaking through the
red tape for quick loan approval.&nbsp;Discover what information lenders need to know
before approving loans and how to save thousands on your next home purchase or refinance. This
information, and more, is contained in our free eBook,<i>&nbsp;
<a href="http://www.lightning-mortgage.com/Answers/eBookRequest.htm">How
To Play The Mortgage Game, and Win!</a></i>
</p></div></div>
